OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780989358
OL,3,CKatie Beattie's family 'ecstatic' her
OL,4,Ccase is being reopened
OL,6,FDetectives have reopened the
OL,7,Finvestigation into the death of 27-
OL,8,Fyear-old woman following a campaign by
OL,9,Fher family, who fear she could have
OL,10,Fbeen murdered.
OL,12,FKatie Beattie was found dead at her
OL,13,Fflat in Lancaster and an inquest was
OL,14,Funable to determine how she died.
OL,16,FPolice enquiries initially concluded
OL,17,Fthere was no evidence to suggest her
OL,18,Fdeath was suspicious.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
