CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780989358
OL,3,CKatie Beattie's family 'ecstatic' her
OL,4,Ccase is being reopened
OL,6,FHowever, her family say they have
OL,7,Funanswered questions and campaigned
OL,8,Ffor a fresh review of the case.
OL,10,FThey have also launched a petition
OL,11,Fcalling for 'Katie Beth's Law', which
OL,12,Faims to reform the way unexplained
OL,13,Fdeaths are investigated.
OL,15,FKatie was found dead on her bed in her
OL,16,Fflat on 1 July 2024, almost fully
OL,17,Fnaked, wearing one sock, with bruises
OL,18,Fon her body.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
