OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780989358
OL,3,CKatie Beattie's family 'ecstatic' her
OL,4,Ccase is being reopened
OL,6,FA neighbour's doorbell footage shows
OL,7,FKatie entering her flat with a man, a
OL,8,Ffew days before she was found dead.
OL,10,FThe family say the man was seen
OL,11,Fleaving again, the day before her body
OL,12,Fwas discovered.
OL,14,FFollowing a Victim's Right to Review
OL,15,Fapplication, Lancashire Police
OL,16,Fconfirmed that the original
OL,17,Finvestigation has been reassessed and
OL,18,Ffurther enquiries are now being
OL,19,Fconducted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
