PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780989358
OL,3,CKatie Beattie's family 'ecstatic' her
OL,4,Ccase is being reopened
OL,6,FKatie's sister Kellie Rhodes said she
OL,7,Fwas on the school run when she got the
OL,8,Fnews in an email. She said: "The first
OL,9,Fthing I did was call my mum.
OL,11,F"We're ecstatic at the news, but
OL,12,Fthere's also a level of frustration
OL,13,Fbecause we shouldn't have had to fight
OL,14,Ffor this."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
