PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780989358
OL,3,CKatie Beattie's family 'ecstatic' her
OL,4,Ccase is being reopened
OL,6,FDavid Beattle, Katie and Kellie's dad,
OL,7,Fadded: "I still cannot understand how
OL,8,Fthey can go into a scene and find a
OL,9,Fyoung girl, naked, deceased, and they
OL,10,Fknow that a guy has been in there for
OL,11,Fthree days, it's on camera - they've
OL,12,Fgot his name.
OL,14,F"(But) they didn't even go and see
OL,15,Fthis guy for over two days, didn't
OL,16,Fbother going to see him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
