FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780989358
OL,3,CKatie Beattie's family 'ecstatic' her
OL,4,Ccase is being reopened
OL,6,F"I've said to everyone, if it was your
OL,7,Floved one, would you just sit and stay
OL,8,Fsilent, would you stop asking
OL,9,Fquestions that you know that should be
OL,10,Fanswered?
OL,12,FMr Beattie added: "What that hurts
OL,13,Fmore than anything is the way Katie
OL,14,Fhas been treated."
OL,16,F"In death, she's been treated like she
OL,17,Fwas nothing, but she was such a loving
OL,18,Fperson."JLancashire Police have
OL,19,Fappealed for anyone with information
OL,20,Fthat could assist the investigation to
OL,21,Fcome forward.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
