CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780989358
OL,3,CKatie Beattie's family 'ecstatic' her
OL,4,Ccase is being reopened
OL,6,FA spokesman said: "The initial
OL,7,Finvestigation has been reviewed
OL,8,Ffollowing a victim right to review,
OL,9,Fand further enquiries are being
OL,10,Fconducted following this.
OL,12,F"Anyone with information that can
OL,13,Fassist those enquiries is asked to
OL,14,Fcall 101 quoting log 1092 of 1 July
OL,15,F2024."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
